abstract: International Monetary Fund warns American stock prices are high and that insurers and mutual funds are prey to financial shocks.
lead_paragraph: The I.M.F. warned that American stock prices were high and that United States insurers and mutual funds were vulnerable to financial shocks.

headline.main: I.M.F. Cautions U.S. on Stocks, Insurance and Mutual Funds
